Freemasons' Who Were Members of the Royal Society - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. FREEMASONS AND THE ROYAL SOCIETY Alphabetical List of Fellows of the Royal Society who were Freemasons
This is an attempt to list Fellows ofthe Royal Society ("FRS") who were freemasons. It has been compiled, on behalf of the Library and Museum of Freemasonry, by Bruce Hogg, assisted by Diane Clements.
